    <detaileddescription>
<sect1 id="group__metric__module_1metric_overview">
<title>Overview</title>
<para>The Metric module provides the <ref refid="classmetric__template" kindref="compound">metric_template</ref> class for implementing custom performance metrics in physics analyses.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="group__metric__module_1metric_types">
<title>Metric Types</title>
<para>Common metric types include:</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Accuracy metrics</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Efficiency measurements</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Physics-specific quantities (mass resolution, etc.)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>ROC curves and AUC</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="classmetric__template" kindref="compound">metric_template</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
</sect1>
